entries.journal_entry_description: Sergean Snopel is sending you to some trainers who can teach you the basics of combat. Heed thier advice.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Good work soldier! Time you learn some close combat techniques. Talk to Rydel in the close combat training room.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: Excellent! I think you know enough now to complete your first mission. Come see me immediately soldier.
